nnoremap <silent> [tbuild]a :wa<CR>:exec g:buildcmd . g:GetBuildAllParams(@%)<CR>
nnoremap <silent> [tbuild]bf :wa<CR>:exec g:buildbackgroundcmd . g:GetBuildFileParams(@%)<CR>
